features: Sturdy Top Lid: A flip-open lid keeps your dirty laundry discreetly hidden from view to keep your bedroom looking neat, while the 3 neutral color choices are sure to compliment any room decor.

Firm & Stable: Constructed from 300D cationic fabric and 1.2mm adhesive coated EVA foam, this laundry hamper is fitted with 2mm cardboard inserts on top and bottom for structure stability. Along with a steel rod and 6 supporting glass fiber pole rods, this hamper is built solid and firm for use.

Easy to Install: Simply put 6 supporting rods into the fixed insert tubes, tie 8 olive buckles into corresponding suspension loops, and it's ready to use. Set up in minutes, and also folds flat for convenient storage when not in use.

Two Large Compartments: With 2 large divided sections, you can easily separate darks and lights, clothing from linens, his and her items, or adult pieces. Two included laundry bags with handles fits onto the hamper firm and tight with drawstring stoppers. Use the handles to easily pull out the removable laundry bags with dirty laundry for wash.

Generous Capacity: The overall dimension of the entire hamper is 23.6'' ( 60cm ) x 13.8'' ( 35cm ) x 25.6'' ( 65cm ), and the capacity is 136L, which can hold 3 - 4 loads of laundry. The capacity of each compartment is 68L, and they both can hold 1.5 - 2 loads respectively.

reviews.reviewText: Great product. Very sturdy and easy to assemble. It comes with bags to easily lift out to take to the laundry room. You can also separate whites and colors.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I didn’t think I was going to like it
reviews.reviewText: We currently had 3 different hampers going and I needed the space. I didn’t think I was going to like the bag part of it but it’s my favorite. We bring laundry downstairs to do and this is so easy. I hate having to undo the little clip things but it only takes a second. I was also afraid the bags would break with my towels in them but so far so good. The actual hamper itself it super light to push around but I wouldn’t recommend picking it up to bring to your washer- it holds too much. The cover is flimsy but I don’t really care. It’s small and cute.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Lifewit Double Laundry Hamper with Lid and Removable Laundry Bags, and I must say, it has greatly improved my laundry organization and storage. This hamper offers a practical and stylish solution for keeping dirty clothes organized and out of sight.One of the standout features of this laundry hamper is its spaciousness. With its large capacity, I am able to easily fit a significant amount of laundry without it overflowing. The hamper is divided into two compartments, allowing me to separate my clothes by color or type. This feature is especially useful for those who prefer to sort their laundry before washing.The lid of the hamper is a great addition as it keeps the laundry out of sight and prevents any unpleasant odors from spreading. The lid is also possible to stay open which is convenient when I need to quickly toss in a last-minute item without having to open the entire hamper.The included removable laundry bags are a practical feature that makes doing laundry a breeze. The bags are made of durable material and are easy to remove and carry to the washing machine. This eliminates the need for additional laundry baskets or bags, saving space and simplifying the laundry process.The hamper is collapsible, which is a major advantage for those with limited storage space. When not in use, I can easily fold it flat and tuck it away in a closet or under a bed. The sturdy handles on the sides of the hamper make it easy to carry, even when it is full of laundry.The overall build quality of the Lifewit Double Laundry Hamper is impressive. The fabric is durable and the stitching is well done, ensuring that it will withstand regular use. The neutral grey color of the hamper is also a nice touch, as it blends well with any home decor.In terms of functionality and convenience, the Lifewit Double Laundry Hamper with Lid and Removable Laundry Bags is a fantastic choice. It offers ample storage space, easy organization, and a stylish design. Whether you need a laundry solution for your bedroom, laundry room, closet, bathroom, or college dorm, this hamper is a reliable and practical option. I highly recommend it to anyone in need of a versatile and efficient laundry storage solution.

reviews.reviewText: Opened and assembled it, when I noticed that the olive buckles that hold the bags in place were missing. No extras in the box and the product page clearly advertises the buckles to hold the bags. I saw reviews with pictures that did include olive buckles, so I returned and ordered another one. Received an identical item without the buckles. Returning once again and buying something else. I ordered the gray version in the Netherlands. If anyone receives one with the buckles after this review let it be known. Otherwise the product does not work
